to\": 1588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stayed on the ground, then rose to one knee, had to call for help.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1627}, {\"ngram\": \"one knee\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was later helped off the field.SUMMERS: Yeah, he seemed to be having a really tough time at the end there, and it's not like what we are used to seeing from him, Brian.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"SUMMERS\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1715}, {\"ngram\": \"a really tough time\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1765}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What can you tell us about what happened?MANN: Yeah, so Noah Lyles has now confirmed in an interview with NBC that he competed after being diagnosed with COVID.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 2006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 1952, \"end\": 1955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9958846236715756, \"rank\": 0.0033001756600749377, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"what happened?MANN\", \"from\": 1873, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 1934, \"to\": 1946}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2005}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, two days ago, he woke up feeling terrible, and he was tested.\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We also have a statement from U.S. Track and Field, saying they were aware of this test.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. Track\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2118}, {\"ngram\": \"Field\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"this test\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They knew that he was running sick today.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They say that was his choice.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his choice\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. Track and Field says they did follow all the necessary safety and health protocols.\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"U.S. Track\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"Field\", \"from\": 2254, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"all the necessary safety and health protocols\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Noah Lyles was around a lot of these other athletes, so there are going to be some big questions asked about this decision to have him included in this race.\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2332, \"end\": 2342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around a lot\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"these other athletes\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"some big questions\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember, Juana, Noah Lyles has suffered from asthma and allergies in the past.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2507, \"end\": 2517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Juana\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"asthma\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2542}, {\"ngram\": \"allergies\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2556}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's talked about that.\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite all this, he still managed to win bronze.SUMMERS: That's right.\", \"from\": 2594, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"SUMMERS\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure we are going to be hearing a lot more about this story.\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2731, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2730}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, I do want to ask you to put his performance into context - what he was attempting to do.\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2827, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2782}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 2788, \"to\": 2795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just how difficult would it have been and how rare would it have been for Lyles to pull off wins in both the 100-meter, as he did earlier in the week, and the 200-meter, which he attempted to do today?MANN: Yeah, winning these two races in one Olympics is so rare.\", \"