m\": \"Juana\", \"from\": 19514, \"to\": 19519}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 19532, \"to\": 19541}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 19548, \"to\": 19557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had that dominant showing Sunday in the 100-meter race.\", \"from\": 19589, \"to\": 19647, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100-meter race\", \"from\": 19628, \"to\": 19646}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But today, he trailed behind Letsile Tebogo of Botswana and Kenny Bednarek of the U.S. - never seriously challenged them for the lead.\", \"from\": 19648, \"to\": 19782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19695, \"end\": 19703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.6398173196786711, \"rank\": 0.5628911863520505, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 19708, \"end\": 19722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 19677, \"to\": 19691}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 19726, \"to\": 19734}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 19773, \"to\": 19781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That powerful late kick that he's famous for never came.\", \"from\": 19783, \"to\": 19839, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That powerful late kick\", \"from\": 19783, \"to\": 19806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, at the finish line, he collapsed.\", \"from\": 19840, \"to\": 19879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 19849, \"to\": 19864}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stayed on the ground, then rose to one knee, had to call for help.\", \"from\": 19880, \"to\": 19949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 19893, \"to\": 19903}, {\"ngram\": \"one knee\", \"from\": 19918, \"to\": 19926}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 19944, \"to\": 19948}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was later helped off the field.SUMMERS: Yeah, he seemed to be having a really tough time at the end there, and it's not like what we are used to seeing from him, Brian.\", \"from\": 19950, \"to\": 20121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 19974, \"to\": 19983}, {\"ngram\": \"SUMMERS\", \"from\": 19984, \"to\": 19991}, {\"ngram\": \"a really tough time\", \"from\": 20022, \"to\": 20041}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 20045, \"to\": 20052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What can you tell us about what happened?MANN: Yeah, so Noah Lyles has now confirmed in an interview with NBC that he competed after being diagnosed with COVID.\", \"from\": 20122, \"to\": 20282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20178, \"end\": 20188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 20228, \"end\": 20231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9913621358636745, \"rank\": 0.0074189683139098215, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 20140, \"to\": 20142}, {\"ngram\": \"what happened?MANN\", \"from\": 20149, \"to\": 20167}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 20210, \"to\": 20222}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 20276, \"to\": 20281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, two days ago, he woke up feeling terrible, and he was tested.\", \"from\": 20283, \"to\": 20353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentenc