": 20764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember, Juana, Noah Lyles has suffered from asthma and allergies in the past.\", \"from\": 20766, \"to\": 20845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20783, \"end\": 20793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Juana\", \"from\": 20776, \"to\": 20781}, {\"ngram\": \"asthma\", \"from\": 20812, \"to\": 20818}, {\"ngram\": \"allergies\", \"from\": 20823, \"to\": 20832}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 20836, \"to\": 20844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's talked about that.\", \"from\": 20846, \"to\": 20869, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite all this, he still managed to win bronze.SUMMERS: That's right.\", \"from\": 20870, \"to\": 20941, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 20912, \"to\": 20918}, {\"ngram\": \"SUMMERS\", \"from\": 20919, \"to\": 20926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure we are going to be hearing a lot more about this story.\", \"from\": 20942, \"to\": 21007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 20996, \"to\": 21006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, I do want to ask you to put his performance into context - what he was attempting to do.\", \"from\": 21008, \"to\": 21103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 21043, \"to\": 21058}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 21064, \"to\": 21071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just how difficult would it have been and how rare would it have been for Lyles to pull off wins in both the 100-meter, as he did earlier in the week, and the 200-meter, which he attempted to do today?MANN: Yeah, winning these two races in one Olympics is so rare.\", \"from\": 21104, \"to\": 21368, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21