, \"from\": 23368, \"to\": 23387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We saw him bound out when he was introduced.\", \"from\": 23389, \"to\": 23433, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was full of that characteristic energy, that showmanship that he is known for, hoping to be the 10th man ever to win both of those races in a single summer games.\", \"from\": 23434, \"to\": 23599, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that characteristic energy\", \"from\": 23449, \"to\": 23475}, {\"ngram\": \"that showmanship\", \"from\": 23477, \"to\": 23493}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10th man\", \"from\": 23529, \"to\": 23541}, {\"ngram\": \"those races\", \"from\": 23562, \"to\": 23573}, {\"ngram\": \"a single summer games\", \"from\": 23577, \"to\": 23598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, why do not you pick it up from here?\", \"from\": 23600, \"to\": 23643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Walk us through what happened.MANN: Yeah, it was clear, Juana, right from the start, that something was different with Noah Lyles.\", \"from\": 23644, \"to\": 23774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23763, \"end\": 23773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 23649, \"to\": 23651}, {\"ngram\": \"MANN\", \"from\": 23674, \"to\": 23678}, {\"ngram\": \"Juana\", \"from\": 23700, \"to\": 23705}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 23718, \"to\": 23727}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 23734, \"to\": 23743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had that dominant showing Sunday in the 100-meter race.\", \"from\": 23775, \"to\": 23833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 100-meter race\", \"from\": 23814, \"to\": 23832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But today, he trailed behind Letsile Tebogo of Botswana and Kenny Bednarek of the U.S. - never seriously challenged them for the lead.\", \"from\": 23834, \"to\": 23968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23881, \"end\": 23889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"score\": 0.9431204621385137, \"rank\": 0.06029924207087962, \"text\": \"Botswana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Botswana\"}, {\"begin\": 23894, \"end\": 23908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 23863, \"to\": 23877}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 23912, \"to\": 23920}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead\", \"from\": 23959, \"to\": 23967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That powerful late kick that he's famous for never came.\", \"from\": 23969, \"to\": 24025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That powerful late kick\", \"from\": 23969, \"to\": 23992}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, at the finish line, he collapsed.\", \"from\": 24026, \"to\": 24065, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 24035, \"to\": 24050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He stayed on the ground, then rose to one knee, had to call for help.\", \"from\": 24066, \"to\": 24135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 24079, \"to\": 24089}, {\"ngram\": \"one knee\", \"from\": 24104, \"to\": 24112}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 24130, \"to\": 24134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was later helped off the field.SUMMERS: Yeah, he seemed to be having a really tough time at the end there, and it's not like what we are used to seeing from him, Brian.\", \"from\": 24136, \"to\": 24307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 24160, \"to\": 24169}, {\"ngram\": \"SUMMERS\", \"from\": 24170, \"to\": 24177}, {\"ngram\": \"a really tough time\", \"from\": 24208, \"to\": 24227}, {\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 24231, \"to\": 24238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What can you tell us about what happened?MANN: Yeah, so Noah Lyles has now confirmed in an interview with NBC that he competed after being diagnosed with COVID.\", \"from\": 24308, \"to\": 24468, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24364, \"end\": 24374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 24414, \"end\": 24417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9752341173911545, \"rank\": 0.022207274758592913, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 24326, \"to\": 24328}, {\"ngram\": \"what happened?MANN\", \"from\": 24335, \"to\": 24353}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 24396, \"to\": 24408}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 24462, \"to\": 24467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, two days ago, he woke up feeling terrible, and he was tested.\", \"from\": 24469, \"to\": 24539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We also have a statement from U.S. Track and Field, saying they were aware of this test.\", \"from\": 24540, \"to\": 24628, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 24553, \"to\": 24564}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. Track\", \"from\": 24570, \"to\": 24580}, {\"ngram\": \"Field\", \"from\": 24585, \"to\": 24590}, {\"ngram\": \"this test\", \"from\": 24618, \"to\": 24627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They knew that he was running sick today.\", \"from\": 24629, \"to\": 24670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They say that was his choice.\", \"from\": 24671, \"to\": 24700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his choice\", \"from\": 24689, \"to\": 24699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. Track and Field says they did follow all the necessary safety and health protocols.\", \"from\": 24701, \"to\": 24789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"U.S. Track\", \"from\": 24701, \"to\": 24711}, {\"ngram\": \"Field\", \"from\": 24716, \"to\": 24721}, {\"ngram\": \"all the necessary safety and health protocols\", \"from\": 24743, \"to\": 24788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Noah Lyles was around a lot of these other athletes, so there are going to be some big questions asked about this decision to have him included in this race.\", \"from\": 24790, \"to\": 24951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24794, \"end\": 24804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around a lot\", \"from\": 24809, \"to\": 24821}, {\"ngram\": \"these other athletes\", \"from\": 24825, \"to\": 24845}, {\"ngram\": \"some big questions\", \"from\": 24872, \"to\": 24890}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 24903, \"to\": 24916}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 24941, \"to\": 24950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember, Juana, Noah Lyles has suffered from asthma and allergies in the past.\", \"from\": 24952, \"to\": 25031, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24969, \"end\": 24979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://d