les\", \"score\": 0.9008106781399461, \"rank\": 0.09648892346310423, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wins\", \"from\": 37308, \"to\": 37312}, {\"ngram\": \"both the 100-meter\", \"from\": 37316, \"to\": 37334}, {\"ngram\": \"the week\", \"from\": 37357, \"to\": 37365}, {\"ngram\": \"today?MANN\", \"from\": 37411, \"to\": 37421}, {\"ngram\": \"these two races\", \"from\": 37437, \"to\": 37452}, {\"ngram\": \"one Olympics\", \"from\": 37456, \"to\": 37468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only nine men have done it before.\", \"from\": 37481, \"to\": 37515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only nine men\", \"from\": 37481, \"to\": 37494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of those men, Jamaican Usain Bolt, did it at three straight Olympics.\", \"from\": 37516, \"to\": 37589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37534, \"end\": 37542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9999281521083195, \"rank\": 7.183205422510763e-05, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those men\", \"from\": 37523, \"to\": 37532}, {\"ngram\": \"three straight Olympics\", \"from\": 37565, \"to\": 37588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time an American pulled this off was Carl Lewis 40 years ago, in 1984.\", \"from\": 37590, \"to\": 37669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37607, \"end\": 37615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9957719098493973, \"rank\": 0.002230326473338918, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 37636, \"end\": 37646, \"title\": \"http://db