 \"from\": 46219, \"to\": 46237}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview\", \"from\": 46280, \"to\": 46292}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID\", \"from\": 46346, \"to\": 46351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said, two days ago, he woke up feeling terrible, and he was tested.\", \"from\": 46353, \"to\": 46423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We also have a statement from U.S. Track and Field, saying they were aware of this test.\", \"from\": 46424, \"to\": 46512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 46437, \"to\": 46448}, {\"ngram\": \"U.S. Track\", \"from\": 46454, \"to\": 46464}, {\"ngram\": \"Field\", \"from\": 46469, \"to\": 46474}, {\"ngram\": \"this test\", \"from\": 46502, \"to\": 46511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They knew that he was running sick today.\", \"from\": 46513, \"to\": 46554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They say that was his choice.\", \"from\": 46555, \"to\": 46584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his choice\", \"from\": 46573, \"to\": 46583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"U.S. Track and Field says they did follow all the necessary safety and health protocols.\", \"from\": 46585, \"to\": 46673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"U.S. Track\", \"from\": 46585, \"to\": 46595}, {\"ngram\": \"Field\", \"from\": 46600, \"to\": 46605}, {\"ngram\": \"all the necessary safety and health protocols\", \"from\": 46627, \"to\": 46672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Noah Lyles was around a lot of these other athletes, so there are going to be some big questions asked about this decision to have him included in this race.\", \"from\": 46674, \"to\": 46835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 46678, \"end\": 46688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around a lot\", \"from\": 46693, \"to\": 46705}, {\"ngram\": \"these other athletes\", \"from\": 46709, \"to\": 46729}, {\"ngram\": \"some big questions\", \"from\": 46756, \"to\": 46774}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 46787, \"to\": 46800}, {\"ngram\": \"this race\", \"from\": 46825, \"to\": 46834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remember, Juana, Noah Lyles has suffered from asthma and allergies in the past.\", \"from\": 46836, \"to\": 46915, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 46853, \"end\": 46863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Juana\", \"from\": 46846, \"to\": 46851}, {\"ngram\": \"asthma\", \"from\": 46882, \"to\": 46888}, {\"ngram\": \"allergies\", \"from\": 46893, \"to\": 46902}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 46906, \"to\": 46914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's talked about that.\", \"from\": 46916, \"to\": 46939, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite all this, he still managed to win bronze.SUMMERS: That's right.\", \"from\": 46940, \"to\": 47011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 46982, \"to\": 46988}, {\"ngram\": \"SUMMERS\", \"from\": 46989, \"to\": 46996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure we are going to be hearing a lot more about this story.\", \"from\": 47012, \"to\": 47077, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 47066, \"to\": 47076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, I do want to ask you to put his performance into context - what he was attempting to do.\", \"from\": 47078, \"to\": 47173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 47113, \"to\": 47128}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 47134, \"to\": 47141}]}, {\"sentence\": \"