\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 52932, \"to\": 52938}, {\"ngram\": \"SUMMERS\", \"from\": 52939, \"to\": 52946}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sure we are going to be hearing a lot more about this story.\", \"from\": 52962, \"to\": 53027, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 53016, \"to\": 53026}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Brian, I do want to ask you to put his performance into context - what he was attempting to do.\", \"from\": 53028, \"to\": 53123, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his performance\", \"from\": 53063, \"to\": 53078}, {\"ngram\": \"context\", \"from\": 53084, \"to\": 53091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just how difficult would it have been and how rare would it have been for Lyles to pull off wins in both the 100-meter, as he did earlier in the week, and the 200-meter, which he attempted to do today?MANN: Yeah, winning these two races in one Olympics is so rare.\", \"from\": 53124, \"to\": 53388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53198, \"end\": 53203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.7429102469820642, \"rank\": 0.3189487223817243, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wins\", \"from\": 53216, \"to\": 53220}, {\"ngram\": \"both the 100-meter\", \"from\": 53224, \"to\": 53242}, {\"ngram\": \"the week\", \"from\": 53265, \"to\": 53273}, {\"ngram\": \"today?MANN\", \"from\": 53319, \"to\": 53329}, {\"ngram\": \"these two races\", \"from\": 53345, \"to\": 53360}, {\"ngram\": \"one Olympics\", \"from\": 53364, \"to\": 53376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only nine men have done it before.\", \"from\": 53389, \"to\": 53423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Only nine men\", \"from\": 53389, \"to\": 53402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of those men, Jamaican Usain Bolt, did it at three straight Olympics.\", \"from\": 53424, \"to\": 53497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53442, \"end\": 53450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9997893695931994, \"rank\": 0.00021066468250144403, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those men\", \"from\": 53431, \"to\": 53440}, {\"ngram\": \"three straight Olympics\", \"from\": 53473, \"to\": 53496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The last time an American pulled this off was Carl Lewis 40 years ago, in 1984.\", \"from\": 53498, \"to\": 53577, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53515, \"end\": 53523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993203869986944, \"rank\": 0.0005547628457239735, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 53544, \"end\": 53554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The last time\", \"from\": 53498, \"to\": 53511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lewis was actually here in the stadium tonight watching.\", \"from\": 53578, \"to\": 53634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lewis\", \"from\": 53578, \"to\": 53583}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 53605, \"to\": 53616}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But again, along with the rest of us, he saw something very different happen - Noah Lyles coming in with a bronze-medal finish.SUMMERS: Brian, while I have you, I do want to ask you about something else that happened here tonight.\", \"from\": 53635, \"to\": 53865, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngr